OL,7,FCCTV footage shows Charles Hartle, who
OL,8,Fwas 17 at the time, holding a large
OL,9,Fknife before running away.
OL,11,FA Derbyshire teenager has been found
OL,12,Fguilty of murdering a young man when
OL,13,Fhe stabbed him once in the chest with
OL,14,Fa "Rambo knife".
OL,16,FFollowing a near-two-week trial at
OL,17,FDerby Crown Court, a jury took less
OL,18,Fthan three hours to unanimously
OL,19,Fconvict Charlie Hartle of the brutal
OL,20,Fkilling of Noah Smedley.
