OL,7,FThe 18-year-old rap music lover, who
OL,8,Fwas 17 at the time he attacked his
OL,9,Fvictim, initially showed no emotion as
OL,10,Fthe foreman of the jury delivered the
OL,11,Fverdict in front of family members of
OL,12,Fthe Ilkeston victim and the
OL,13,Fdefendant's own loved ones.
OL,15,FBut within a minute of hearing the
OL,16,Fnews, he leaned forward and began to
OL,17,Fsoftly sob, holding his head in his
OL,18,Fhands.
