OL,7,FThe trial heard how Hartle, nicknamed
OL,8,F"Lil Cee", and three friends arranged
OL,9,Fto meet Mr Smedley to buy cannabis
OL,10,Ffrom him on the evening of December
OL,11,F28, last year.
OL,13,FThe victim arrived on his scooter at
OL,14,Faround 8.15pm and after the deal had
OL,15,Ftaken place, in Rose Avenue, off
OL,16,FHeanor Road, Ilkeston, the defendant
OL,17,Fmoved forward and pushed the fearsome
OL,18,Fblade into the victim's chest before
OL,19,Fhe and his friends fled the scene.
