OL,8,Fheard how following the fatal
OL,9,Fstabbing, Hartle first went to a
OL,10,Fnearby party where his girlfriend was
OL,11,Fand then fled to Derby before his
OL,12,Ffather drove to the city centre and
OL,13,Fbrought him home to Stanley.
OL,15,FThe accused was wearing different
OL,16,Fclothing to what he had on at the time
OL,17,Fof the stabbing and the knife and his
OL,18,Fphone were not on him and have never
