OL,7,FThe defendant was then driven to
OL,8,FIlkeston police station where he was
OL,9,Farrested for murder. Mr Langdale said
OL,10,Fin a prepared statement given to the
OL,11,Fpolice who questioned him: "Firstly, I
OL,12,Faccept responsibility for inflicting
OL,13,Fthe injury on Noah Smedley. There is a
OL,14,Fhistory to this, and Noah and I did
OL,15,Fnot get on.
OL,17,F"He has, in the past, made numerous
OL,18,Fthreats to me and made disparaging
OL,19,Fcomments. He has threatened me with
OL,20,Fviolence.
